The way you perform one task is a reflection of how you will perform all tasks, so focus on excellence in everything you do.
Losers talk about wanting to win but don't take action, while winners take action and do whatever it takes to achieve success.
Having pride in being the best and being dominant amongst your teammates is key to success.
You must be willing to separate yourself from others through hard work, dedication, and a strong work ethic.

You must be willing to put in the time and effort to develop a strong work ethic and a growth mindset in order to achieve success.
